metadata.name: We all float
metadata.description:
I found one of the original houses from the movie "IT" so I grabbed my camera and started shooting.

I had an idea, a concept to add the clown from the movie into the scene, and started playing around with the colors, tones and vibes.

I wanted to create a unique story with my concept, I also wanted to create a concept that I would be afraid of.

This Halloween Haunt 2022
